<p>
<seg id=1> The ground control officers for the team that were attempting to circumnavigate the world by balloon said that, the three men should fly towards the air space under control of China.  Then they will continue towards the East crossing the Pacific Ocean. </seg>
<seg id=2> On Tuesday, this three men team in the balloon wandered out of the cleared flight path and caused a political incident. </seg>
<seg id=3> Chinese Officials once ordered them to land in Tibet where China is in charge.  However, China withdrew this order after negotiations by the British and American Diplomats. </seg>
